nodes.text: The Prince Militaire was the de facto leader of the Hiveborn, the government of the Paataatus species. During the Nikardun campaigns, an unidentified Paataatus held the rank. The Prince Militaire staged a fake attack on Senior Captain Mitth'raw'nuruodo's forces before covertly requesting Thrawn's assistance in freeing the Paataatus from the Nikardun Destiny during the skirmish above Nettehi, which Thrawn provided.
